fields.name: CapacityReservationLevel
fields.description: The capacity reservation level in GB per day. Returned for the Capacity Reservation Service Tier.

fields.name: DefaultRetention
fields.description: The default retention for the Service Tier, in days.

fields.description: True if the Service Tier is enabled for the workspace.

fields.name: MaximumRetention

fields.name: MinimumRetention
fields.description: The minimum retention for the Service Tier, in days.

fields.name: ServiceTier
fields.description: The name of the Service Tier.
